OL,3,CWaste disposal company to pay #16k for
OL,4,Cillegally dumping on floodplain
OL,6,FA waste disposal company has been
OL,7,Fordered to pay more than #16k after
OL,8,Fpleading guilty to dumping thousands
OL,9,Fof tonnes of waste on a floodplain in
OL,10,FDevon.
OL,12,FDTM Grab Hire Ltd dumped 3,490 tonnes
OL,13,Fof soil, stones and rubble at an
OL,14,Fillegal site in Kingsteighton between
OL,15,FJanuary and September 2021.
OL,17,FThe 'muck-away' company was fined
OL,18,F#13,653 and will pay costs of #2,821
OL,19,Fplus a victim surcharge.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
