OL,3,CWaste disposal company to pay #16k for
OL,4,Cillegally dumping on floodplain
OL,6,FAccording to the Environment Agency
OL,7,Fthe waste on the illegal dump would
OL,8,Fhave significantly increased flood
OL,9,Frisk in the area.
OL,11,FThe Kingsteighton site was shut down
OL,12,Fin 2022 and the landowner, Christopher
OL,13,FGarrett from Kingsteignton, was jailed
OL,14,Fin 2024.
OL,16,FGarrett has been called "the worst
OL,17,Foffender the Environment Agency has
OL,18,Fseen" in Devon and Cornwall after he
OL,19,Fburned demolition waste and buried
OL,20,Flarge quantities of asbestos on the
OL,21,Fland next to his home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
