OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779383153
OL,3,CWaste disposal company to pay #16k for
OL,4,Cillegally dumping on floodplain
OL,6,FHe earned hundreds of thousands of
OL,7,Fpounds from allowing people to
OL,8,Fillegally dump on his land despite
OL,9,Fmultiple warnings and an enforcement
OL,10,Fnotice from the Environment Agency.
OL,12,F"We have now successfully prosecuted
OL,13,Fthe landowner of this illegal site,
OL,14,Fplus two waste carriers who
OL,15,Fcontributed to the deposit of soil and
OL,16,Fstone," a spokesperson for the
OL,17,FEnvironment agency said.
